d0f4ee2bfb6ecda346f0a5cced69dd444c4a9b","tid":1878623,"uid":10722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T18:49:17.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"dd37bdafed3ce39a2d3d6f4408b2e46f29a0205e","tid":1878623,"uid":5818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T18:52:26.000Z","msg":"可以到地獄手撕鬼子啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db4a7b48f21b0c0639a223500f320080ef47d44","tid":1878623,"uid":34241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T18:53:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>感染及傳染病專科醫生曾祈殷指出，退伍軍人桿菌的潛伏期約2至10日，若患者均曾於近期使用彩虹站出入，不排除該站就是「播毒」元兇。他續指，<span style=\"color: red;\">冷卻水塔若有病菌，多數影響中央冷氣系統或冷熱水管，不排除站內各個出口、以至月台等均會帶菌，「尤其彩虹站月台仲會開冷氣」</span>，認為港鐵應審慎起見，關閉彩虹站全面檢查及消毒。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n水塔既散熱水如果含菌<br />\n1. 水塔風扇運作時, 散熱水從水缸蒸發 吹向大氣, 空氣傳播<br />\ne.g. 水塔出風吹向/近民居 <br />\n(應該唔會太近, EMSD有例規管要隔一段距離, 太近唔會批准你開工, <br />\n偷到雞起完, 亦唔會比你運作)<br />\n<br />\n2. 直接接觸到散熱水, e.g. 散熱水喉漏水<br />\n<br />\n而中央冷氣行chiller 提供冷凍水, <br />\n用黎將站內空氣降溫既係chilled water冷凍水<br />\n唔係condensing water 散熱水<br />\n2個水系統基本上係完全隔開, 唔會溝埋<br />\n所以講話「開冷氣會令水塔既菌進入經過冷卻既空氣」, 係戇鳩"},{"pid":"7dc3116d60d90628f135fb4a515b8e5f01cec24f","tid":1878623,"uid":93383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0becb28b91f88727bb9c9fe10725576b958ee7c9","tid":1878623,"uid":59955,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T17:55:26.000Z","msg":"病徵同武肺咁撚似既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T18:55:46.000Z","msg":"退休軍人症一直都係atypical pneumonia 既其中一個可能性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd36dcf73f3d8826b39eba324ed8fe64e67a23d","tid":1878623,"uid":2886