rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雪梨唐人街確診兩宗退伍軍人症個案<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t45.1600-4/cp0/q90/spS444/p261x260/85893224_23844416676390399_6630615192109580288_n.png.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_oc=AQnLacLiftslU6tKf4lrnHo7gcFjLb1JnBu9DHUuDye5pSNoc4SJbcFA8AlcKqsMui4&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=81d914bfa842f35ae92a4e4c4be3108c&amp;oe=5ECA51F5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft45.1600-4%2Fcp0%2Fq90%2FspS444%2Fp261x260%2F85893224_23844416676390399_6630615192109580288_n.png.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_oc%3DAQnLacLiftslU6tKf4lrnHo7gcFjLb1JnBu9DHUuDye5pSNoc4SJbcFA8AlcKqsMui4%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D81d914bfa842f35ae92a4e4c4be3108c%26oe%3D5ECA51F5&h=3b520956&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39e958ab0a89b0650dc98efaa1047284caa96e5f","tid":1878623,"uid":28202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a4f5afc7bfc8f66ad71bde952e0645bd85f8674","tid":1878623,"uid":28202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"560624e505877f6191889eca68788946f0f81b7e","tid":1878623,"uid":217189,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T17:23:41.000Z","msg":"爆 爆 爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T20:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雪梨唐人街確診兩宗退伍軍人症個案<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t45.1600-4/cp0/q90/spS444/p261x260/85893224_23844416676390399_6630615192109580288_n.png.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_oc=AQnLacLiftslU6tKf4lrnHo7gcFjLb1JnBu9DHUuDye5pSNoc4SJbcFA8AlcKqsMui4&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=81d914bfa842f35ae92a4e4c4be3108c&amp;oe=5ECA51F5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft45.1600-4%2Fcp0%2Fq90%2FspS444%2Fp261x260%2F85893224_23844416676390399_6630615192109580288_n.png.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_oc%3DAQnLacLiftslU6tKf4lrnHo7gcFjLb1JnBu9DHUuDye5pSNoc4SJbcFA8AlcKqsMui4%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D81d914bfa842f35ae92a4e4c4be3108c%26oe%3D5ECA51F5&h=3b520956&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T20:59:27.000Z","msg":"七號電視台報道，雪梨東南部衛生區表示，當局調查當地在本年較早前出現的兩宗退伍軍人症個案時，發現雪梨 Haymarket 區域兩座冷卻塔內發現軍團菌。<br />\n<br />\n目前該兩座冷卻塔已停止運作，當局呼籲最近兩星期曾到過 Haymarket 一帶的民眾留意自己是否有出現退伍軍人症癥狀。<br />\n<br />\n衛生區表示，兩名患者為分別 40 多歲及 70 多歲的男子，目前已康復，而目前前往 Haymarket 亦不再有感染退伍軍人症的風險。<br />\n<br />\n但當局強調，過往兩星期曾經前往當地的人士應留意是否有感染軍團菌。<br />\n<br />\n衛生區公共衞生副主任謝珀（Vicky Sheppeard）醫生表示，退伍軍人症癥狀可以在感染後長達十天才出現，癥狀包括發燒、發冷、咳嗽及呼吸急促。<br />\n<br />\n她指出，情況可導致更嚴重感染，包括肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n謝珀醫生在一份聲明中說：「醫護人員一般透過胸部 X 光檢查、尿液檢驗及在醫院進行抗生素治療為病者進行診斷。」<br />\n<br />\n退伍軍人症不會透過人傳人感染，但大規模爆發一般是由於大型建築物空調系統的水冷卻系統出現軍團菌而出現。<br />\n<br />\n瀏覽更多最新時事資訊，請登上廣東話節目 Facebook 專頁，或訂閱廣東話節目 Telegram 頻道。"},{"pid":"fa9326543d5fc2bb916a1d167fbe48b74414c754","tid":1878623,"uid":283222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae0962f64cfd2ff1cc1a9ff03d23a7ed9be39a16","tid":1878623,"uid":230511,"like":150,"dislike":1,"score":149,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T17:27:38.000Z","msg":"退伍軍人症令坊間歧視退伍軍人<br />\n世衛點解唔改名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T23:18:43.000Z","msg":"交差感染可叫(武肺退軍症)或(正武肺軍人)，註冊先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03747d04059f6de4c58271fae3998afb990056b9","tid":1878623,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}